quoridor.model

Class Wall

  • java.lang.Object
    • quoridor.model.Square
      • quoridor.model.Wall
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Wall
extends Square
implements java.io.Serializable
    Wall class, extends from Square. This class represents a special kind of Square, that players can place on the grid to block other player's pawn to move freely on the grid.
